I&#x27;ve got a python project where I&#x27;ve been pretty naughty with long lines containing sql queries.<p>I found that running this tool over it resulted in some strange new lines.<p>For example, this was my old hideously long line:<p>query_qual = &quot;INSERT OR REPLACE INTO Qualifying (poleid, seasonid, race_week_num, carclassid, pole) values (%s%s, %s, %s, %s, %s)&quot; % (race[u&#x27;seasonid&#x27;], race[u&#x27;race_week_num&#x27;], race[u&#x27;seasonid&#x27;], race[u&#x27;race_week_num&#x27;], race[u&#x27;carclassid&#x27;], pole)<p>Changed to this:<p>query_qual = &quot;INSERT OR REPLACE INTO Qualifying (poleid, seasonid, race_week_num, carclassid, pole) values (%s%s, %s, %s, %s, %s)&quot; % (
		race[u&#x27;seasonid&#x27;], race[u&#x27;race_week_num&#x27;], race[
				u&#x27;seasonid&#x27;
		], race[u&#x27;race_week_num&#x27;], race[u&#x27;carclassid&#x27;], pole)
